Stroke←{
    steno←⍵~' '
    banks←,[0.5]⌿↑2↑⊂⍣(2=≡⍺)⊢⍺
    (left middle)←(0⊥⍴)¨¯1↓banks
    (letters numbers)←↓⊃,/banks
    Error←{⎕SIGNAL 11}
    indices←('-'≠steno)/+\⊃{
        drop←+/⍵
        '-'=⍺:⍵,Error⍣(index<middle)        ⊢index←drop-⍨left+middle
              ⍵,Error⍣(index>drop-⍨≢letters)⊢index←letters⌊⍥(⍺⍳⍨drop∘↓)numbers
    }/(⌽steno),⊂⍬
    ('#'=letters)∨⍣(∨/⍵∊numbers)⊢indices∊⍨⍳≢letters
}
